ID: TC_002
Title: Register user with invalid email
Priority: High
Severity: Medium
Preconditions:
* User not logged in
Test Data: 
* Name: Vlad Test (for all sets)
Set 1 - Missing @:* Email: vladtest.gmail.com * Expected: Email validation error 
Set 2 - Space in email: * Email: vlad test@gmail.com * Expected: Email validation error 
Set 3 - Incomplete domain: * Email: vladtest@ * Expected: Email validation error 
Set 4 - Invalid domain: * Email: vladtest@h * Expected: Email validation error

Steps:
1. Navigate to “https://automationexercise.com/login”
2. Verify "New User Signup!" visible
3. Enter name in “Name” field
4. Enter invalid email (from Test Data Set)
5. Click "Signup" button
6. Verify error message displayed near email field
7. Verify "New User Signup!" form still visible (not proceeded)

Expected result:
1. Email validation error message displayed (e.g., "Invalid email format" or browser validation)
2. Signup button does not proceed to next step
3. "New User Signup!" form remains visible
4. No account created in system
5. User stays on /login page
6. No navigation to account creation form

Actual result:
Status: Not Run